Would you try this? 😳💦 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting worlderlust.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @worlderlust

Devil’s Pool is a natural pool of water that’s situated atop of Victoria Falls, renown for being among the largest waterfalls in the world. Right on the edge of this massive waterfall, a calm pool of water forms.

This is known as the Devil’s Pool Victoria Falls. And daring visitors can actually swim in this pool straddling the edge of Victoria Falls!

📽 @abenafrica
📍Zambia and Zimbabwe
🎶 Ikson - Apart
